latestIgtvVideos.title: YOUniq Pink Frosted Look
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Gradation of pink tones, popping purple shimmer , faded eyeliner with fluttering eyelashes. The YOUniq Frosted Pink Look. 💄

You can definitely beautify your look, structure your face, set illusion with makeup but that beautification also comes from within. A happy , stressfree face can make the makeup look fresh. We all have different battles to fight but one should know how to put that stress load off the body and mind. 💫💫
This is 1 big Anti Aging Pill apart from all the skin care products. A reduced Stress helps in slow aging process and good longevity. ❤
.
